    [adminuser@oracle_linux7 ~]$ ping6 2022:dd10::e84a:94ff:fea6:9d00
    PING 2022:dd10::e84a:94ff:fea6:9d00(2022:dd10::e84a:94ff:fea6:9d00) 56 data bytes
